## 6. Integraciones y Automatizaciones

### 6.1 OAuth Social (Google + Microsoft)

```javascript
// backend/src/config/passport.js (fragmento)
passport.use(new GoogleStrategy({
  clientID: process.env.GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID,
  clientSecret: process.env.GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET,
  callbackURL: '/api/v1/auth/google/callback',
  scope: ['profile', 'email', 'https://www.googleapis.com/auth/gmail.readonly']
}, async (accessToken, refreshToken, profile, done) => {
  const user = await findOrCreateUser(profile, 'google', { accessToken, refreshToken });
  return done(null, user);
}));
```

### 6.2 WhatsApp Business (Meta Cloud API)

```javascript
// Webhook handler
app.post('/webhooks/whatsapp', async (req, res) => {
  const { entry } = req.body;
  for (const change of entry[0].changes) {
    if (change.value.messages) {
      const msg = change.value.messages[0];
      await whatsappQueue.add('process-inbound', {
        from: msg.from,       // número del cliente
        text: msg.text?.body,
        type: msg.type,       // text, image, document
        timestamp: msg.timestamp
      });
    }
  }
  res.sendStatus(200);
});

// Worker: busca contacto y registra comunicación
whatsappQueue.process('process-inbound', async (job) => {
  const { from, text } = job.data;
  const contact = await findContactByPhone(from);
  await communicationsService.create({
    type: 'whatsapp',
    direction: 'inbound',
    body: text,
    contact_id: contact?.id,
    metadata: { whatsapp_number: from }
  });
});
```

### 6.3 Integración de Email (IMAP + SMTP)

- **Envío:** SendGrid / SMTP propio via Nodemailer
- **Recepción/Sync:** IMAP via `imapflow` — sincroniza bandeja de agente, asocia emails a contactos por dominio/email match
- **Thread tracking:** Pixel de tracking en emails enviados desde el CRM

